ANALYSIS
This bill enables highway authorities to license curbside electric vehicle charging devices in
public rights-of-way, establishes procedures for adjacent host property electrical supply and
reimbursement,clarifiesenforcementandsitingstandards,andaffirmsthatownersandoperatorsof
suchchargingdevicesarenotpublicutilities.
