METHODOLOGY:
This bill authorizes highway authorities (state or municipal) to license curbside electric vehicle
charging devices in public rights-of-way, establishes procedures for adjacent host property
electrical supply and reimbursement, clarifies enforcement and siting standards, and affirms
thatownersandoperatorsofsuchchargingdevicesarenotpublicutilities.
